where people mock you.

02:02.880 --> 02:05.760
- And you don't even realize it.
- Michael, I'm a magi...

02:05.880 --> 02:07.680
I see what you did.

02:07.800 --> 02:11.039
You're not dressed yet? I thought you
were working for me today at the office.

02:11.160 --> 02:13.840
