13:30.120 --> 13:31.098
- What did he say?

13:31.099 --> 13:33.760
- If I clean it up, it's
not really a sentence.

13:33.880 --> 13:36.840
<i>And so, George Sr. made another call.</i>

13:36.960 --> 13:40.200
Kitty's on the loose. I need you
to make something disappear for me.

13:40.320 --> 13:43.320
just some books in that cooler
marked "Maddas. "

13:43.440 --> 13:45.880
<i>- Great.
- George Sr. hung up...</i>

13:45.960 --> 13:48.880
<i>confident that his problems
would finally be taken care of.</i>

13:48.960 --> 13:50.880
Hey, LittleJustice.

13:50.960 --> 13:53.680
You, uh, painted your shoes red.

13:53.760 --> 13:56.960
Call me the Tin Man.
I'm a Friend of Dorothy's now.

13:57.080 --> 14:00.400
<i>- And she wants to see you.
- And back at the office...</i>

14:00.480 --> 14:04.000
<i>Lindsay arrived with her daughter
and her mounting suspicions.</i>

14:04.120 --> 14:06.840
Mom says she sent Nana on a cruise.

14:06.920 --> 14:08.680
You're still on this?
How much was in those birthday cards?

14:08.800 --> 14:11.520
It's not about the money,
Michael. It's about Nana.

14:11.640 --> 14:13.440
I think Mom sent her
to a nursing home...

14:13.560 --> 14:16.200
some gray, windowless room...
against her will.

14:16.320 --> 14:19.640
- So what was it like out there today?
- Nice. Sunny.

14:19.720 --> 14:21.440
Wow.

14:21.560 --> 14:23.960
So, how do you think Gob's gonna
make this yacht disappear?

14:24.040 --> 14:26.520
Well, I'll be working here,
so I guess I'll never know.

14:26.600 --> 14:28.680
The only real way to find out
how it's done...

14:28.800 --> 14:30.600
is to sneak on the boat
while he does it.

14:30.720 --> 14:33.520
But if he makes it disappear,
won't everyone see me standing there?

14:33.600 --> 14:38.640
Let's just sit quietly and consider
how ridiculous that statement was.

14:40.800 --> 14:43.040
Anyways, if it was me,
that's what I would do.

14:43.160 --> 14:44.960
I wanna check out
Mom's financial activity.

14:45.080 --> 14:47.040
Call her banks,
maybe run a hospital search.

14:47.160 --> 14:49.240
<i>It's gonna mean a lot of
hard work, but I'll put somebody on it.</i>

14:49.320 --> 14:52.120
George Michael.

14:52.200 --> 14:54.440
Where is George Michael?

14:54.560 --> 14:56.400
<i>In fact, at Maeby's suggestion...</i>

14:56.480 --> 14:59.000
<i>George Michael was off to visit
his Uncle Gob.</i>

14:59.120 --> 15:00.960
Hi, Uncle Gob.
I came by to see...

15:01.080 --> 15:03.040
if you need any help
with your magic show.

15:03.160 --> 15:03.592
- Great.

15:03.593 --> 15:06.240
- I think it's so great
that you're doing this.

15:06.360 --> 15:09.720
- I'm prepping right now.
- How'd you get my Dad's permission?

15:09.800 --> 15:11.520
<i>Suddenly, Gob remembered
the promise he had made...</i>

15:11.640 --> 15:13.480
<i>to stay away from Michael's son.</i>

15:13.600 --> 15:16.000
None of your damn business.
Get the hell out of here.

15:16.120 --> 15:17.960
- What?
- You don't have the magic in you!

15:18.080 --> 15:19.880
You never did!
You don't have it here!

15:21.520 --> 15:24.480
So take a look. It's the last time
you're gonna see these.

15:26.720 --> 15:28.840
- Sorry, kid, more than you'll ever...
- What?

15:28.960 --> 15:29.684
<i>Beat it!</i>

15:29.685 --> 15:33.240
- As Gob was forced to send
away someone he loved...

15:33.360 --> 15:36.000
<i>- You'll be missed.
- George Sr. was forced to visit...</i>

15:36.120 --> 15:39.640
<i>someone he had once tried
to shove out of a moving car.</i>

15:40.960 --> 15:43.720
- Welcome.
- You're Dorothy?

15:43.840 --> 15:46.720
I thought the two of us
could talk, man-on-man.

15:48.000 --> 15:50.840
<i>I'm afraid I'm serious.</i>

15:50.960 --> 15:52.840
<i>I bought you.</i>

15:54.680 --> 15:56.569
- Remember to let it
steep for five minutes.

15:56.570 --> 15:57.319
- Oh, dear God.

15:57.320 --> 15:59.200
I've been in this family
for 16 years...

15:59.320 --> 16:01.440
and I don't think we've
ever had a conversation.

16:01.560 --> 16:03.800
- I'm not gonna discuss this.
- You hate me.

16:03.880 --> 16:06.360
Yeah, I do hate you.
You took my daughter...

16:06.480 --> 16:08.920
my precious little girl...
and moved her away...

16:09.000 --> 16:12.120
and now I'm here, and I am afraid
I will never get her back.

16:12.200 --> 16:14.680
Afraid. You're afraid.

16:14.760 --> 16:17.120
Fear has turned into hate.

16:17.240 --> 16:20.480
So Frightened Inmate #2
isn't frightened at all.

16:20.600 --> 16:24.440
He's angry.
He's a crabby old coot...

16:24.520 --> 16:26.440
and he needs love...

16:26.560 --> 16:28.640
just like everyone.

16:28.760 --> 16:30.680
Get your...
hands off of me.

16:30.760 --> 16:33.520
Shh. Don't be scared.

16:40.920 --> 16:43.480
<i>And on the beach,
the show was beginning.</i>

16:49.400 --> 16:54.080
<i>Any magician can make
the queen of diamonds disappear...</i>

16:54.160 --> 16:57.480
but what about a whole boat?

