18:02.560 --> 18:06.000
And got rid of the evidence.
How about a "good job"?

18:06.080 --> 18:09.320
<i>Seeing a window of opportunity,
Lucille made a startling announcement.</i>

18:09.440 --> 18:11.840
- Nana was on that yacht!
- What?

18:11.960 --> 18:14.400
<i>- You killed Nana!
- She's lying!</i>

18:14.520 --> 18:16.640
Nana wasn't on that yacht.
She's fine.

18:16.760 --> 18:19.240
<i>She's been dead for six months.
- Lindsay had learned this information...</i>

18:19.360 --> 18:20.319
<i>- For about six months.</i>

18:20.320 --> 18:22.200
- when she spoke to the
family's personal banker.

18:22.280 --> 18:24.560
<i>Later, fearing that
Lindsay was onto her...</i>

18:24.640 --> 18:26.480
<i>Lucille went to the bank herself.</i>

18:26.560 --> 18:29.640
<i>There must be somewhere I can put
this money where it can't be touched.</i>

18:29.760 --> 18:31.800
I suppose you could keep it
in your purse.

18:31.880 --> 18:34.880
Very funny, but I'm
not carrying a purse.

18:35.000 --> 18:36.960
<i>Where's the money, Mom?
I want the money.</i>

18:37.080 --> 18:40.600
You can't have it.
It's in a trust fund for Annyong.

18:40.680 --> 18:42.240
<i>- Annyong.
- No one can touch it but me...</i>

18:42.360 --> 18:45.000
and I retain control of it
until he's 18.

18:45.120 --> 18:47.280
I don't know what's more offensive...
the fact you didn't tell us...

18:47.360 --> 18:51.240
<i>about our grandmother's death
or that you sunk a $ 700,000 yacht!</i>

18:51.360 --> 18:54.120
<i>Stop lecturing me.
I just lost my mother.</i>

18:54.240 --> 18:56.320
I'm so glad George Michael
wasn't here to see any of this.

18:56.440 --> 18:58.720
Maeby, where is George Michael?

18:58.840 --> 19:03.440
Um, well, if he's not here, I'd just
have to say he's probably on the yacht.

19:03.520 --> 19:05.320
On the yacht?

19:05.440 --> 19:07.800
<i>In fact, George Michael
had boarded the yacht.</i>

19:07.920 --> 19:11.320
<i>But when he saw the evidence
of Gob's lifestyle...</i>

19:11.440 --> 19:14.520
<i>he realized that this perhaps
was not the life he wanted.</i>

19:14.600 --> 19:17.000
<i>While Kitty went in search
of retribution...</i>

19:17.120 --> 19:19.600
<i>in the form of the files
in the cooler.</i>

19:19.680 --> 19:22.800
<i>George Michael's a good kid.
I'm sure he's at the office.</i>

19:22.880 --> 19:24.720
Right. I told him
to stay away from you.

19:24.800 --> 19:28.240
- I told you to stay away from him!
- I tried. I told him to get out.

19:28.320 --> 19:30.160
Bluth Company.
George Michael speaking, not Kitty.

19:30.240 --> 19:33.200
- Thank God you're there.
- I don't need a real spring break.

19:33.280 --> 19:36.840
