19:42.280 --> 19:44.440
- You're fired.
- Really?

19:44.520 --> 19:46.680
Can you fire people?

19:46.800 --> 19:48.640
Yeah. Go have a spring break.

19:48.760 --> 19:51.080
Thanks, Dad.

19:51.200 --> 19:52.800
Are you sure you're gonna
be okay without Kitty?

19:52.920 --> 19:55.360
Don't you worry.
She'll turn up.

